    "description": "<br><br><strong>《A House of Thieves|窃贼横行》</strong>是一款关卡式的潜行喜剧恐怖游戏。在游戏中窃贼拿着购物清单要购物的地方不是超市，而是别人家里。<br>设想你想做一些意大利面，但你的番茄酱用完了。而你也不是那种去超市买东西会付钱的人。你会怎么做？<br>没错！带上你的购物清单，闯入邻居家并拿走他们的东西！<br><br>人气独立VR游戏<i>There is a Thief in my House</i>的PC版。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >优秀的重玩性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>清单中的每个物品都是随机的<br></li><li>每次重玩一个关卡，物品的位置都会改变<br></li><li>房主会在屋内随机走动——AI的移动没有任何系统</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/e127683d25818b1b4c27dfc79cea7c0e.poster.avif?t=1666990270\" width=332 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/e127683d25818b1b4c27dfc79cea7c0e.webm?t=1666990270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/e127683d25818b1b4c27dfc79cea7c0e.mp4?t=1666990270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可解锁道具</h2>list]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>完成关卡的速度越快，获得的星星越多<br></li><li>获得一定数量的星星就可以解锁新道具</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/cbf7cf52be7c95af825a445b809aa88a.poster.avif?t=1666990270\" width=444 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/cbf7cf52be7c95af825a445b809aa88a.webm?t=1666990270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506760/extras/cbf7cf52be7c95af825a445b809aa88a.mp4?t=1666990270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人游戏</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>支持最多4名玩家与AI对抗或3名玩家与1名玩家对抗。<br></li><li>扮演房主可放置陷阱捉住窃贼。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta